Brewers 8, Dodgers 2
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   MILWAUKEE (AP) -- Jeromy Burnitz and Luis Lopez each drove in three runs,
leading the Milwaukee Brewers over the Los Angeles Dodgers 8-2 Thursday. Geoff
Jenkins homered, doubled, singled and scored three runs. Lopez homered and
Burnitz doubled twice and singled.
</P>
